OL,6,FOn Friday afternoon they confirmed he
OL,7,Fhad been released on bail with
OL,8,Fconditions that prevent him from
OL,9,Fentering certain educational
OL,10,Festablishments, or the Amman and
OL,11,FGwendraeth Valley areas. Bail
OL,12,Frestrictions also include a curfew,
OL,13,Fand prevent him having unsupervised
OL,14,Faccess to social media.
OL,16,FIn a statement, Gwent Police said:
OL,18,F"We carried out a search during the
OL,19,Farrest, and no offensive weapons were
OL,20,Ffound. He remains in police custody at
OL,21,Fthis time as our enquiries continue.
