OL,6,F"We understand the level of concern
OL,7,Ffrom parents in the area today, but
OL,8,FI'd like to thank the public and the
OL,9,Fschool for following protocol,
OL,10,Fremaining calm and relaying any
OL,11,Fconcerns they had to us.
OL,13,F"These actions allowed us to act
OL,14,Fquickly, make an arrest, safeguard
OL,15,Fpupils and reassure the community.
OL,17,F"The school is now no longer in
OL,18,Flockdown and parents and guardians are
OL,19,Fcollecting their children."
