OL,6,FA spokesperson for Blaenau Gwent
OL,7,FCouncil said:
OL,9,F"Ebbw Fawr Learning Community's
OL,10,FSecondary Campus staff responded
OL,11,Fquickly and calmly to activate well-
OL,12,Festablished emergency planning
OL,13,Fprocedures that ensure the safety and
OL,14,Fwell-being of learners and staff.
OL,16,F'The school and Local Authority have
OL,17,Fbeen working closely with Gwent Police
OL,18,Fto ensure the continued safety of
OL,19,Feveryone on the school site today and
OL,20,Fto reassure concerned parents."
